Name: Air Marty
About the game: Join Marty and his family on the vacation of a life time! -A multitude of minigames that all lead to a new branch in the story. -64 endings all with a variety of hand crafted art styles. -A roller coaster of emotions! -Exciting 'Streamlined' gameplay with each story branch lasting only minutes makes everyone a speedrunner here! -A cast of whacky characters at every twist and turn!
